Dormio Installation
===================

Installing from git
===================

> git clone git://github.com/tf198/dormio.git dormio
> cd dormio
> # need to get the Phorms library if you want auto form generation
> git submodule update --init

Documentation is not included in the repo - you can build it if you have phpDocumentor on
your system with 
> make api_docs

Installation from tarball
=========================

> wget http://???/dormio/dormio-latest.tar.gz
> tar zxvf dormio-latest.tar.gz
> mv dormio-X.X.X dormio

Running Examples
================

> cd dormio
> php docs/examples/usage.php
> php docs/examples/forms.php